# Keep the manuscript and supplementary out of the Zenodo software/data archive.
# These are the *paper*, versioned by the journal/preprint DOI, not the software
# release. Excluding them from `git archive` means editing the manuscript no
# longer changes the software archive, so the Zenodo software DOI only needs to
# be re-minted on real code/data releases. The files remain in the Git repo.
docs/manuscript.md export-ignore
docs/supplementary.md export-ignore
